@TennisStats.API_HostAddress = http://localhost:5012

### =====================================================
### Import Controller - Data Import Endpoints
### =====================================================

### Health Check - Verify Import Service is Available
GET {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Get Import Status
GET {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/status
Accept: application/json

###

### Import WTA Players (paginated, with 1 second delay between requests)
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/players?association=0&maxPages=100&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### Import ATP Players
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/players?association=1&maxPages=100&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### Import WTA Tournaments (2020-2025)
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/tournaments?association=0&startYear=2020&endYear=2025&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### Import ATP Tournaments (2020-2025)
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/tournaments?association=1&startYear=2020&endYear=2025&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### Import WTA Rankings (current)
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/rankings?association=0
Accept: application/json

###

### Import ATP Rankings (current)
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/rankings?association=1
Accept: application/json

###

### Full Historical Import - WTA (2020-2025) - LONG RUNNING!
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/full?association=0&startYear=2020&endYear=2025&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

### Full Historical Import - ATP (2020-2025) - LONG RUNNING!
POST {{TennisStats.API_HostAddress}}/api/import/full?association=1&startYear=2020&endYear=2025&delayMs=1000
Accept: application/json

###

